  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pilot study of a wearable gas and sweat skin sensor
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is exploratory and deploys two wearable sweat and gas sensors
      which detect the composition of sweat proteins and volatile gases emitted from the skin in
      healthy subjects and patients with atopic dermatitis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
